---
---

<section id="chi-sono" class="py-24 bg-navy relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative Background Glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-orange/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none -mr-48 -mt-48"
  >
  </div>

  <div
    class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center relative z-10"
  >
    <!-- Immagine -->
    <div class="fade relative">
      <div
        class="bg-white/5 rounded-[40px] overflow-hidden aspect-4/5 relative border border-white/10"
      >
        <img
          src="/stefano.jpg"
          alt="Stefano Moretti"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top filter grayscale-20 hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
        />
        <!-- Badge disponibile -->
        <div
          class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-navy/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl px-5 py-3 flex items-center gap-3 whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          <span
            class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[#25D366] rounded-full animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_10px_#25D366]"
          ></span>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Disponibile ora</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-white/40">· Empolese Valdelsa</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Decorazione -->
      <div
        class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-24 h-24 bg-orange/10 rounded-3xl -z-10 blur-sm"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-navy-light/20 rounded-3xl -z-10"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Testo -->
    <div class="fade d1">
      <div
        class="inline-block bg-white/10 text-orange text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-5 py-2 rounded-full mb-8 border border-white/5"
      >
        Chi sono
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-[1.1] mb-8">
        Trasparenza e valore<br /><span class="text-orange">per la tua</span> energia.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
          Mi chiamo <strong class="text-white font-bold">Stefano Moretti</strong
          >. Oltre ad un consulente, cerco di essere una <strong
            class="text-white font-bold">risorsa trasparente</strong
          > per le persone che scelgono di affidarsi alla mia competenza nell'Empolese
          Valdelsa.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed text-base font-light italic border-l-2 border-orange/30 pl-6"
        >
          "Il mio lavoro è proteggere la tua tranquillità energetica. In un
          mondo di offerte aggressive, io punto sulla chiarezza e su un rapporto
          umano che non teme confronti."
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-base font-light">
          A differenza della freddezza dei call center, <strong
            class="text-white font-bold"
            >offro una presenza costante e diretta</strong
          >. Costruisco con i miei clienti un legame basato sulla stima
          reciproca, diventando il loro punto di riferimento per ogni necessità.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-10">
        <span
          class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/50 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-xl"
          >🏠 Privati</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/50 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-xl"
          >🏢 Aziende</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/50 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-xl"
          >🏪 PMI & Negozi</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-white/5 border border-orange/20 text-orange/60 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-xl"
          >⚡ Luce</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-white/5 border border-orange/20 text-orange/60 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-xl"
          >🔥 Gas</span
        >
        <span
          class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/50 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-xl"
          >📍 Toscana</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
